建议创建数据库视图v_dealer_info，整合经销商代码与省份信息：

CREATE VIEW v_dealer_info AS
SELECT 
    dealer_code,
    province,
    fed_level
FROM radar_source_2024
WHERE province IS NOT NULL;

同时修改前端API接口，在返回经销商列表时关联查询视图：

@app.route('/api/dealers/list', methods=['GET'])
def get_dealers_list():
    dealer_info_result = db.session.execute(
        db.text("SELECT dealer_code, province, fed_level FROM v_dealer_info")
    )
    dealer_info_map = {}
    for row in dealer_info_result:
        dealer_info_map[row[0]] = {'province': row[1], 'fed_level': row[2]}
